enb_long_title: Tenth Conference of the Parties to the UN Framework Convention on Climate Change
sentences: Audited financial statements for the biennium 2002-3: This issue was first addressed by the SBI on Tuesday, 7 December.
SBI adopted conclusions on Tuesday, 14 December, and agreed to forward a draft decision to the COP.
On Friday, 17 December, the COP adopted the decision, which takes note of the audited financial statements.
